The paper deals with decoding algorithms for algebraic geometric (AG) codes, which are commonly studied in information theory (cs.IT) and coding theory (cs.CC). The paper also mentions the use of techniques from list decoding, which is a topic in theoretical computer science (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY).
